parking services partnered with parkmobile reservation to provide a service that allows users to make parking reservation for event at sjsu by using the parkmobile app reservation feature. get the parkmobile app to use the system, register online at https://parkmobile.io or download the mobile app. once registered, use the mobile app, internet, or parkmobile’s toll free number (877-727-5730) to pay for parking (note: if you don’t have a “smart phone” you can still set up a parkmobile account and pay for parking by calling the toll free number). watch a video demonstration . select parkmobile reservation how to [pdf] for instruction in pdf. 